      • ExcelSheetDefault

        public ExcelSheetDefault(org.apache.poi.ss.usermodel.Workbook workbook,
                         TranslateService translateService,
                         DgFmService fmService,
                         java.lang.String excelSheetName)
        Constructor used to print an Object in a separate excel sheet. The sheet will be created based on object name that is exported. excelSheetName would be the name of the excel and the recommended value is Class.getSimpleName() toLowerCase.
